, "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/regional-guide-schools-prepare-tsunamis", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "4d6d23e5ecc78171d76beb61c70623c17a55b3cfd9cdb75024d6ad55c3843095"}}, "hash": "dbfb863ae21bd45611b03a57d86816058e3e5d755b0f5049e21d74bd528c55d9", "text": "Design and layout: Tiina Joosu-Palu and Zohra Moazzam Khan Cover page photo: UNDP Papua New Guinea Copyright \u00a9 UNDP 2019 United Nations Development Programme Bangkok Regional Hub 3rd Floor United Nations Service Building Rajdamnern Nok Avenue Bangkok 10200, Thailand Tel: +66 2 304-9100 Fax: +66 2 280-2700 Website: http://www.asia-pacific.undp.org/content/rbap/en/home/programmes- and-initiatives/SchoolTsunamiPreparedness.html 2 ACRONYMS BRH CO DRR GCDS GoJ ICG/IOTWS ICG/PTWS IOC IOTIC IRIDeS ITIC JICA LIPI MOU UNDP UNESCO UNV Bangkok Regional Hub Country Office Disaster Risk Reduction Global Centre for Disaster Statistics Government of Japan Intergovernmental Coordination Group for the Indian Ocean Tsunami Warning and Mitigation System Intergovernmental Coordination Group for the Pacific Tsunami Warning and Mitigation System Intergovernmental Oceanographic Commission Indian Ocean Tsunami Information Centre International Research Institute of Disaster Science International Tsunami Information Centre Japan International Cooperation Agency Indonesia Institute of Sciences Memorandum of Understanding United Nations Development Programme United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization United Nations Volunteer 3 TABLE OF CONTENTS 1. INTRODUCTION 4 2. SEVEN STEPS OF TSUNAMI EVACUATION DRILLS 6 STEP 1: HEAR A LOUD SOUND SIMULATING AN EARTHQUAKE 7 STEP 2: DROP. COVER. HOLD 7 STEP 3: EVACUATE HAZARD ZONES 9 STEP 4: MEET AT THE ASSEMBLY AREA 11 STEP 5: CONFIRM HEADCOUNT 11 STEP 6: SIMULATION COORDINATOR SIGNALS END OF DRILL 12 STEP 7: ASSESS D